commands to run this repo code:

docker compose up -d → starts only demo-service, otel-collector, jaeger
docker exec -it jaeger rm -rf /badger/data/*   // to run just clear the jaeger trace storage 
docker restart jaeger
docker restart otel-collector  // it is for to reset the otel-collector 

docker compose --profile manual build --no-cache  (build not from cache) 
docker compose --profile manual up -d loadgen → starts loadgen when you want
docker compose run --rm loadgen    (to run specific container  also show logs on console)
docker compose logs -f loadgen

to see results in jaeger UI: http://localhost:16686/search
to see results in otel-collector UI: http://localhost:8888/metrics


docker compose down -v   (stop all conatiners)
docker rm loadgen
docker compose ps -a ( to check service status up/exited)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------


* there are two otel-collector-config files*
1 otel-collector-config-headbased.yaml -  this configuration is head based sampling policy 
2 otel-collector-config-tailsampling.yaml - this configuration use tailsampling policy


to use which ever sampling policy copy that in otel-collector-config.yaml. then run below commands
docker compose up -d --force-recreate otel-collector
docker compose run --rm loadgen  || docker compose --profile manual up -d loadgen


